online_mean = OnlineMean()
for n in nums:
    online_mean.add(n)
assert online_mean.rounded_mean(places=places) == out
pytest.mark.parametrize('nums,places,out', (([0, 1], 0, 0), ([0, 1], 2, 0.5
    ), ([1, 1], 0, 1), ([1, 1], 2, 1), ([1, 1, 2], 0, 1), ([1, 1, 2], 2, 
    1.33), ([1, 2, 2], 0, 2), ([1, 2, 2], 2, 1.67)))
